name: Lingga - a love story (1)
description:
When instant noodles met teh botol, tea in a glass bottle - Indonesia's most favourite drink. A love story of instant street culinary for decades.

Lingga series. A bowl of IGOR (mI-GOReng, instant fried noodles with egg) in a shape of the iconic "penis" bottle opener from Bali. And raise your glass and drink all the stories of IGOR life
